  "detailed_description": "《武林志2》的故事发生在《武林志1》的十年前，外域武林三大门派天外天、五行宫、金刚门入侵中原，天山派与江湖诸派惨遭灭门。主角本是天山派弟子，机缘巧合之下成为了江湖上最出名的杀手。本作讲述的即是主角联合武林各路英雄豪杰驱逐外域武林，开创新门派，重整中原武林秩序的故事。<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2></strong><br><strong>【无缝地图 告别加载】</strong><br>最新无缝大地图技术，配合轻功、游泳的动作，目之所及皆能至。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/cbb89c4e1627499091d973b3b67c6461.poster.avif?t=1664413608\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/cbb89c4e1627499091d973b3b67c6461.webm?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/cbb89c4e1627499091d973b3b67c6461.mp4?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【沙盒武侠 快意恩仇】</strong><br>开放式地图探索机制，游戏中所有NPC均可被攻击，给你自由的武侠世界体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/2ccfab0327b862803d7085b70dc0ae86.poster.avif?t=1664413608\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/2ccfab0327b862803d7085b70dc0ae86.webm?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/2ccfab0327b862803d7085b70dc0ae86.mp4?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【即时战斗 畅爽连招】</strong><br>纯正的无锁定战斗机制，配合4种战斗中可切换的武器及上百种招式，让玩家可以自由连招打出自己的专属连击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/8218aa8ba655a7c8b31d5c6aa510a465.poster.avif?t=1664413608\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/8218aa8ba655a7c8b31d5c6aa510a465.webm?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/8218aa8ba655a7c8b31d5c6aa510a465.mp4?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【内功组合 阴阳调和】</strong><br>游戏有着数十种内功，而不同内功之间会互相冲突，会相辅相成，一些独特内功还有自己的路数，能给你的所有武学带上如拉近、震飞等武侠表现力十足的特殊效果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/b0ca8e734dbce7228ed25cda3fbe4bd7.poster.avif?t=1664413608\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/b0ca8e734dbce7228ed25cda3fbe4bd7.webm?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/b0ca8e734dbce7228ed25cda3fbe4bd7.mp4?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【捏脸系统 千人千面】</strong><br>游戏有捏脸系统，体型编辑功能和纸娃娃装备系统，玩家可以打造专属于自己的侠客。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/deeacc68865ff42a3dd310d8afd8a558.poster.avif?t=1664413608\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/deeacc68865ff42a3dd310d8afd8a558.webm?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465890/extras/deeacc68865ff42a3dd310d8afd8a558.mp4?t=1664413608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
